text: White-barred can refer to: * White-barred wrasse * White-barred piculet * Charaxes brutus, the white-barred emperor or white-barred charaxes * Recurvaria leucatella, the lesser budmoth or white-barred groundling moth * Acraea encedon, the common acraea, white-barred acraea or encedon acraea * Synanthedon spheciformis, the white-barred clearwing
title: White-barred
